---
title: Breaded Pork Ranch Burgers with Potato Wedges and Dill Pickles
description: In this twist on a classic Iowa-based sandwich – the Iowa Skinny – we've traded tenderloin cutlets for a breaded burger patty! Breadcrumbs play two parts: keeping the pork patty tender and adding that perfect crunch to every bite!
